'''Nuriya Benɣebriṭ-Remɛun''' d tasertayt tadzayrit tlul g 5 Meɣres 1952, seg 5 Mayu 2014 ar 1 yebrir 2019 nettat tella d taneɣlaft n ussegmi n [[Lezzayer]].

Send ad d-tuɣal taneɣlaft, tella ttetwellih CRASC (Centre national de recherche en anthropologie sociale et culturelle).

Gma-s n jeddi-s, [[Si Qeddur Benɣebriṭ]], yella yiwen seg imdanen i d-yesnulfan [[Tamezgida n Paris]].

